1. Moja *sestra* ima crnu kosu. (My *sister* has black hair.)
2. *Sestra* je glavna medicinska sestra u bolnici. (*Sister* is the head nurse at the hospital.)
3. Danas ću posetiti svoju *sestru* u Beogradu. (Today I'm going to visit my *sister* in Belgrade.)
4. Kada sam bio bolestan, *sestra* me je negovala. (When I was sick, my *sister* took care of me.)
5. Moja prijateljica je kao *sestra* meni. (My friend is like a *sister* to me.)
6. *Sestrama* je bilo dosadno pa su otišle u šoping. (*Sisters* were bored, so they went shopping.)
7. Ona se slaže sa svojim *sestrama* veoma dobro. (She gets along very well with her *sisters*.)
8. *Sestre* su zajedno otišle na putovanje. (*Sisters* went on a trip together.)
9. Mnogo mi je lakše kada imam podršku svojih *sestara*. (It's much easier for me when I have the support of my *sisters*.)
10. U našoj porodici ima pet *sestara* i jedan brat. (There are five *sisters* and one brother in our family.)